title: THE IANN DIOR INTERVIEW — BFFs EP. 55
description:
On this week's pod, we're joined by Iann Dior to talk about his upcoming album, losing himself over quarantine, and his road to success. We recap this week's headlines including Pete Davidson and Kim Kardashian potentially dating, Logan Paul punching a fan, and judge various influencers' Halloween costumes.
